* [x] Forfeit handling
* [x] Turn timer logic

## ✅ Implemented Features

- Homepage with game creation/joining
- Hexagonal grid rendering
- Turn-based gameplay with timer
- Win detection (6 in a row)
- Player forfeit
- Local game storage (same browser only)
- Start button for ready players

## 🚨 Known Limitations

1. **Single Browser Only**: Games stored in localStorage don't sync across browsers or incognito mode
2. **No Real-time Sync**: Players must refresh to see updates
3. **No Authentication**: Anyone can claim any username
4. **No Game Persistence**: Games lost on browser clear

