## 🔄 Next Priority: Backend Setup

To enable cross-browser multiplayer, need to implement one of:
1. **Node.js + Socket.io** - WebSocket-based real-time sync
2. **Firebase/Supabase** - Serverless backend with real-time listeners
3. **WebRTC** - Peer-to-peer communication
